  "detailed_description": "<strong>Welcome to test your reflexes and patience. Enjoy transforming from a regular green guy to a little dasher!</strong><br><br>* Control our little, green, and cute character to finish every level. <br>* There are 10 levels that are different and playable during the game.<br>* Lots of funny and educational signs will be waiting for you in the game!<br><br>Are some levels hard for you? Don't worry I added a Pass Level button on the pause menu, but please don't use it unless it's necessary.<br><br><u>Here are a couple of things to do in-game:</u><br><br><strong>-></strong> Just run and jump at the right time  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576550/extras/7fe3793a21a370927ec7f06ac19c4bea.apng?t=1720213236\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576550/extras/7fe3793a21a370927ec7f06ac19c4bea.poster.avif?t=1720213236\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=24 /></picture></span><br><br><strong>-></strong> Don't die (optional) <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576550/extras/729b07177d086f189dfb894948446442.apng?t=1720213236\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576550/extras/729b07177d086f189dfb894948446442.poster.avif?t=1720213236\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=24 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576550/extras/ac367d1cdd81863b57389a9af75b06c7.apng?t=1720213236\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576550/extras/ac367d1cdd81863b57389a9af75b06c7.poster.avif?t=1720213236\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=24 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576550/extras/dc3b00404ce97971e29fec1c83956579.apng?t=1720213236\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576550/extras/dc3b00404ce97971e29fec1c83956579.poster.avif?t=1720213236\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=24 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576550/extras/3c658d78ec2634f2dd8deedd442cb37c.webp?t=1720213236\" width=18 height=18 /></span><br><br><strong>-></strong> Read all signs to learn game mechanics (please) <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576550/extras/da5ec99542123d506e022b88b8f3d0ce.webp?t=1720213236\" width=18 height=18 /></span><br><br><strong>-></strong> No need to collect coins, but collect anyway because I made an effort to add them. <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576550/extras/18d843bf1a35bd18874c915ce6eaf19f.apng?t=1720213236\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576550/extras/18d843bf1a35bd18874c915ce6eaf19f.poster.avif?t=1720213236\" class=\"bb_img\" width=18 height=18 /></picture></span><br><br><br>Unnecessary fact: This project is the first game I have ever created. <br><br>I hope you will enjoy it while playing. <br><strong>There is a small message in the last level for you all.</strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576550/extras/14fc01c5b28b3ec9bc40a8546fe515e2.webp?t=1720213236\" width=18 height=18 /></span><br><br>Finally, I'm wondering about your opinions after finishing the game. <br>Please, feel free to share your thoughts about the game.<br><br>Creator: Dogukan Onder",
